task.summary: Big refactoring. Also explosions became faster.

Big-big commit. Added shaders. racks are transparent now. Craks are only on block now. Textures in own-for-each files. Fire, smoke and blocks are drawing by specilal-for-each shaders. And some other stuff (I don't remember).
Fixed Peter's fixes. Now all works fine.
Tales depend from time (not for drawing-count) now.
Guns fix, Tale fix, some graphic optimisations.

Editing can be started by HUD.**. (and closed by button, ^_^) Animation feature: background become lighter slow. Coefs for connection length. new Bug: if be once disconnected one piece from ship, ship disappears o_O. TODO: roll for editmode.
Rolling in editing, selected model has orange border, World and OurWorld are different classes now.
